    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Smack Monkey:</u> Never Stop Smacking</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Reject humanity. Return to monkey.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Smack Monkey is a satisfying precision platformer where you climb fast! <i>(and fall even faster...)</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191540/extras/8e8df5123e02f096082c5e765eee4f70.apng?t=1741382200\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191540/extras/8e8df5123e02f096082c5e765eee4f70.poster.avif?t=1741382200\" class=\"bb_img\" width=168 height=126 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mr. Marcus Monkey</strong> slept in and is now late for his date with his hot monkey girlfriend!!!! <i>AAAAAAAAAAHHHHHH!!!!!</i> Jump, climb and smack your way to the top of <strong>Sunset Mountain</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>~Mr. Marcus Monkey has the shmoves~</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press <strong>&quot;Smack&quot;</strong> to do a horizontal smack jump on the ground or vines!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press <strong>&quot;Smack&quot;</strong> before you smash into a wall to do a vertical smack climb!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press <strong>&quot;Jump&quot;</strong> three times in succession to perform a triple jump!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you slip up however... You might tumble down! Save yourself from losing progress by smacking or jumping out of a slide, before it's too late!!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191540/extras/bc9e158de150cd39be4d7f2e6ff27c17.apng?t=1741382200\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191540/extras/bc9e158de150cd39be4d7f2e6ff27c17.poster.avif?t=1741382200\" class=\"bb_img\" width=192 height=192 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your buddy <strong>Eric the Toucan</strong> will &quot;guide&quot; you on your quest to scaling Sunset Mountain. He also says mean things sometimes, but he's got a good heart. (At least, so I've been told...)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191540/extras/228889cddab602c2ec2e9924b6d0cfe9.apng?t=1741382200\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191540/extras/228889cddab602c2ec2e9924b6d0cfe9.poster.avif?t=1741382200\" class=\"bb_img\" width=384 height=222 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also... watch out for bananas, frostadiles, snakes and ice... They'll mess ya up!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen to legendary classical tracks from the great minds of Debussy, Erik Satie and more,  performed live by a trained monkey on a marimba.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock different monkey colors by reaching the top fast enough!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also I heard that if you smack your way into hidden locations, you might even find a secret frog or two... <i>ribbit</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has speed running features! There's a built-in timer, an optional tutorial and variable endings based on completion time.</p></li></ul>",
